{{for|the Irish newsreader|Bryan Dobson}}

'''Brian Dobson''' is the third of three brothers, the others being [[Paul Dobson|Paul]] and [[Michael Dobson (actor)|Michael]], who are well-known for their talent as voice actors. 

Before beginning his career as a voice over actor in [[1979]], Brian was known for his talents as a disc jockey at Monty's Showroom Pub, where he was in charge of 8-10 exotic dancers a week.

